track.name: Weary Blues
comments: Wow, sounds just like Howlin' Wolf...hahahahaha! You know, I think it just might be within the realm of possibilities that that is her natural voice and that she is not trying to sound like Billie at all! Anyhow, she is a wonderful singer in her own right. This is a terrific song and the album is wonderful.
"This would be fabulous as a Film soundtrack... it would be great if such options were explored. This sound is icon. Needs to be mainstream. " [2] Beautiful. ♥♥♥
And thank goodness for those who have the courage to humbly take the baton.
can't touch the lady...but definitely a very talented disciple
